channel.description:
BJP is a major political party in India, founded in 1980. Currently BJP is the leading party of NDA which is in power as the Union Government of India.
The party is associated with ideology of Nation First and advocates conservative social policies, self reliance, foreign policy driven by a nationalist agenda and strong defence.
channel.title: I support BJP
